$32,999.00 + Tax. Freight & Prep Included! New Hurricane SunDeck Sport 185 w/90HP Yamaha 4stroke. Monaco Blue Full Hull Sides. Ski Tow Bar. Grey Interior. Snap-In Gary Mat & Blk Sea Mat. Digital Depth Finder. Upgraded Fusion BT Stereo. Full Cover. New Load-Rite Aluminum I-Beam Trailer. LOADED!

No limits, fun and performance come standard in a design that’s easy to maneuver, tow and store. Enjoy more comfort and capacity with an open floor plan, lounge seating and windscreen helm.

Every Day Action Hero

Unleash the entertainment champion within you, with the do it all and have it all sport infused performance of SunDeck Sport. From lazy days to crazy days, the versatility, capability and adventurous personality welcomes any boating passion with open arms.

Features may include:

Round Out Your Entertainment

Available side-mount table is the perfect space and shape to grab a bite, sip a cold one or share a laugh. Versatile design lets you choose when it’s time to idle and gather with friends or accelerate and move out to the next adventure.

Spray It Down And Live It Up

The action never stops thanks to a conveniently located stern wash down system. Quickly clean the swim deck platform, water toys, sandals and sandy feet as the party migrates from the beach to the open water.

Easy To Navigate

The sporty design of our helm allows you to take control of the water with confidence thanks to its intuitive design. Distinctive red-needle sweep gauges keep tabs on performance; premium center-mounted fish finder makes every cast count and convenient recessed phone holder ensures you’re always connected.

21' Monaco Luxury Triple-Toon! 10yr Bow to Stern Warranty. Oversized Bimini. Fusion BT Stereo. Quilted Upholstery Pattern. LED Docking Lights. Lowrance Colored Fish/Depth Finder. Windscreen. LOADED!

Versatile and stylish, our 19 to 25-foot Monaco Cruise models offer room for more with L-shaped seating, a standard table to gather with friends and an extended stern swim platform.

Features may include:

The Best Conversations Start Here

  • Gather around the table, settle into the comfortable aft-located L-shape couch, secure your drink into a cup holder and let the day unwind. Good times and good conversation go hand-in-hand and the Monaco Cruise is ready for both.

Change Happens Fast

  • Pop up the integrated mid-ship changing room and slip into something more appropriate. Whether its watersports and sun or an afternoon lunch at a lakeside resort, the convenient Cruise equipped changing room is just what you and your guests need to be ready for day of anything.

Storage and More

  • You won’t find a cluttered deck here. With space to bring along everything you need for a day on the water and more, the Monaco Cruise is flush with integrated storage capabilities. Enjoy abundant underseat and convenient chaise storage spaces along with easy access helm with nearby USB charging port and under-helm with improved obstruction free access.

The New Shape of Control

  • You won’t find cookie-cutter, me-too consoles on a Godfrey. Our designers employed computer aided design technology and were inspired by recent trends in automotive interiors to develop our next-generation helm. The defined shape with textured touch-zones and intuitive layout allows for an optional large-screen Garmin 742 screen and new obstruction free under-helm access.

Smooth Operator

  • The refined yet classic lines of a Monaco Cruise perfectly blend comfort, premium details and a build quality designed for generations into a boat that only looks expensive.
  • Excellent cruising performance
  • Additional storage space with the standard toy box on the stern platform
  • Spacious stern seating with bow loungers to fit the whole family

description:
The NITRO® Z18 is America’s best-selling fiberglass bass boat AND the official boat of Major League Fishing® because it balances power and fishability in a ready-to-win package. It’s built around our revolutionary NITRO® VORTEX TECHNOLOGY™ (NVT™) hull with the RAPID PLANING SYSTEM™ transom, giving you a smooth, dry ride, quick holeshot and precise handling.

The massive bow deck is laid out with one purpose—catching fish. And the NITRO-exclusive Z-CORE™ seating makes cruising across the lake in heavy chop a comfortable as possible. With a 24-volt Minn Kota® trolling motor and new Lowrance® HOOK Reveal 5C fishfinder, it’s truly a bass boat for everyone.

The TRACKER® BASS TRACKER® Classic XL is a value-packed, all-welded aluminum boat that brings back the good ol' days of the original TRACKER boats. It’s rigged and ready to help you and your family make memories that will last for generations to come.

The Classic XL is outfitted with a Minn Kota® trolling motor, Lowrance® color fishfinder and custom-matched GALVASHIELD® Impact trailer, so you can head straight to the lake. And like every all-welded TRACKER, it’s backed by the TRACKER Promise—the best factory warranty in aluminum boats.

  • Backed by the TRACKER® PROMISE—the best factory warranty in aluminum boats
  • NEW DIAMOND COAT™ 2.0 Black Diamond or Royal Red finish w/industry-exclusive powder coat & clearcoat for brilliant durability
  • Reliable & efficient Mercury® FourStroke outboard
  • Factory rigged w/a Minn Kota® trolling motor & Lowrance® color fishfinder
  • Rugged, all-welded, 2-piece aluminum hull w/pressed-in strakes & chines
  • Generous storage below driver & passenger seats, under bow deck & in aft deck
  • 2 folding, TRACKER®-made fishing seats w/bow & aft seat bases
  • 9-gal. (34.07 L) aerated, rotomolded livewell in front of console
  • Port side rod holders w/organizer for 4 rods to 7' (2.13 m)
  • Custom-matched TRACKER®-made trailer w/GALVASHIELD® Impact protection

In addition to celebrated NITRO® performance, the Z20 Pro includes popular upgrade options at an incredible value.

The brain of this fish-catching powerhouse is two Humminbird® HELIX™ fishfinders networked together and to a Minn Kota® Ultrex® trolling motor, giving you the control to find fish and stay on them while the competition is still searching.

The basis of the Z20 is our NVT™ hull—a design that uses a series of parabolic curves instead of traditional strakes, resulting in a hull that's faster, gives more lift while on plane and improves handling. The Z-CORE™ seating system with Force Flex suspension and contoured frame, designed in collaboration with Kevin VanDam, gives you the most comfortable ride in our history. And it comes fully rigged on a custom-matched, tandem-axle trailer with GALVASHIELD® Impact corrosion and chip protection.

dealerListings.description:
The TRACKER® TOPPER™ 1236 jon boat is easy to transport on top of a car or in a truck bed—and it can still accommodate 2 anglers and their gear! It also features a wider, 36" bottom for added stability. Crafted from rugged 5052 aluminum alloy, the TOPPER 1236 is backed by a 3-year structural limited warranty, ensuring the quality TRACKER is known for.

The stable and compact 1236 is reinforced with transverse extruded aluminum ribs, pressed-in strakes, corner transom braces, underseat foam for flotation and a durable powder-coat finish. With this versatile and lightweight boat, you'll be able to enjoy the great outdoors anytime, anywhere. An optional trailer is available.

  • Durable Forest Green powder-coat finish for good looks & long life
  • Flat bottom riveted aluminum hull
  • .050 gauge 5052 marine aluminum alloy
  • Pressed-in chines for strength & tracking stability
  • Corner braces at transom
  • 2 bench seats (center & aft)
  • Underseat foam for flotation
  • Bow & stern handles for lifting 
  • 3-year limited warranty on riveted structure
  • Available w/optional trailer

dealerListings.description:
With the TAHOE® 450 TF, you get an affordable runabout that is easy to tow and extremely versatile.

At 18’ 5” long with an overall package weight of just over 3,000 lbs., the 450 TF is great for families towing their boat to and from the water. But, don’t let its nimble size deceive you. This boat still packs features for ski-and-fish versatility.

For the sport enthusiasts, aft swim platforms with a telescoping ladder and plenty of storage for gear do just the trick. And for the anglers, a Minn Kota® trolling motor, aerated livewell and removable fishing chairs all come standard.

  • POWERGLIDE® fiberglass hull w/HYDROSTEP® lifting strakes
  • Minn Kota® PowerDrive™ 12V, 55-lb. (24.9 kg) thrust, 54" (1.37 m) shaft, removable trolling motor w/wireless remote
  • Fore & aft non-skid fishing positions w/2 removable fishing seats w/storage bags
  • 10-gal. (37.85 L) insulated, aerated livewell
  • Stereo w/Bluetooth® input & 2 speakers
  • Driver & passenger bucket seats w/slide & swivel
  • Full-width aft seating w/insulated molded-in storage & space for optional removable cooler
  • Full-width aft sunpad w/storage, including ski rope holder
  • Port & starboard aft swim platforms w/4-step telescoping boarding ladder
  • Custom-fit, single-axle trailer w/powder-coated GALVASHIELD® Impact, disc brakes & swing-away tongue
